name: $example
desc: Returns: Whether a resource is included in the guide as part of the rules defined by the guide, or just as an example of a resource that conforms to the rules and/or help implementers understand the intent of the guide.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Whether a resource is included in the guide as part of the rules defined by the guide, or just as an example of a resource that conforms to the rules and/or help implementers understand the intent of the guide.

name: $::name
desc: Returns: A human assigned name for the resource. All resources SHOULD have a name, but the name may be extracted from the resource (e.g. ValueSet.name).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A human assigned name for the resource. All resources SHOULD have a name, but the name may be extracted from the resource (e.g. ValueSet.name).

name: $description
desc: Returns: A description of the reason that a resource has been included in the implementation guide.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A description of the reason that a resource has been included in the implementation guide.

name: $acronym
desc: Returns: A short code that may be used to identify the resource throughout the implementation guide.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A short code that may be used to identify the resource throughout the implementation guide.

name: $exampleFor
desc: Returns: Another resource that this resource is an example for. This is mostly used for resources that are included as examples of StructureDefinitions.
